title: 9-1-1 and American Crime Story Versace Live Stream w/ Special Guest Casey Soper
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Hey Marygirl, you should do a new video on American Horror Story season 8. There are new cast members announced !. Looking forward to future videos ;)!.

description:
Host is MaryGirl Moody with special guest Casey Soper. We're talking the season finales for Fox's new series 9-1-1 and American Crime Story; The Assasination of Gianni Versace. Bring your lunch and take your shoes off, it's time to talk about our favorite shows.
